- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction): The paper involves the development of a tool to make texture creation more efficient and user-friendly, which is a common topic in human-computer interaction.
- cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory): The paper involves the creation of textures for 3D objects, which is a common topic in game design and development.
